		{
			dependencies: [
				"52759072B76D79FD"
				"497584693F232C18"
			]
			description: [
				"  Stop for a moment and think: have you ever wondered how four wooden planks suddenly become a magic workbench with the ability to unite nine components? This table is your true first altar, the heart of all creation, and perhaps the game’s oldest cosmic joke."
				""
				"  To build it, plant a &asapling&r at the center of the ritual. Place &64 planks&r on the surrounding stands and dance for it a little. Yes, crouch repeatedly like a lunatic. Once it grows, the aura itself will see fit to grant you your first Crafting Table."
				""
				"  After that, you will be able to craft more of them through the new 3x3 grid, without needing to repeat the ritual."
				""
				"&7&o— Ah, yes. A magic tree, a ridiculous dance, and presto: civilization’s greatest mystery solved.&r&r"
			]
			id: "565979255D303596"
			rewards: [{
				id: "3AFCE7B6565FF9F0"
				item: "minecraft:cherry_sapling"
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "square"
			size: 1.1d
			subtitle: "The Crafting Table."
			tasks: [{
				id: "724F9153947F879D"
				item: "minecraft:crafting_table"
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Where Every Journey Truly Begins"
			x: -7.0d
			y: -1.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["565979255D303596"]
			description: [
				"  So, no, the table was never going to transform planks and sticks into tools out of pure goodwill. First, it needs direction. A plan. Preferably one drawn by someone only slightly more organized than you."
				""
				"  For the next step, take a few blank pages from the back of this book. You only need to place me alone in the crafting grid. Relax, I will not take it personally. Just try not to overdo it. &4I'm Serious.&r"
				""
				"  Use those pages to make a Blueprint. Think of it as the first sketch of intent: a crude memory of the tool you want to create. It will not be powerful. It will not be beautiful. But it will be yours, and for now, that is enough."
				""
				"  You have already managed the table. Now it is time to make something that answers your will."
				""
				"&7&o— Some tools forget their owners. And some were never made to. Let us find out which kind you are about to craft.&r&r"
			]
			hide_dependency_lines: false
			id: "64F2B2761FBEB6BD"
			rewards: [{
				id: "137FC647ACAD0D5D"
				item: "minecraft:stick"
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "square"
			tasks: [{
