		{
			dependencies: ["2B403653AED97321"]
			description: [
				"  The presence of the aether begins to reveal itself in the world in subtle ways. Trees touched by golden fibers start to react over time, exposing luminous flaws in their leaves. This is more than decoration, it is the first step toward directly handling aura."
				""
				"  Take the gold you gathered and combine it with flowers to create Brilliant Fibers. Place those fibers into the leaves of a nearby tree and wait. Once the entire canopy has changed, break the transformed leaves to collect Golden Leaves. They will be essential for producing Gold Powder, the central ingredient of your first ritual."
				""
				"  And since I know you are impatient: if you shake this book hard enough, you may manage to knock a little gold dust loose from between its pages. A cheap trick, yes, but enough to get things moving while you wait for the full transformation."
				""
				"&7&o— Gold does not grow on trees... except when, through sheer irony, it does.&r&r"
			]
			icon: "naturesaura:gold_fiber"
			id: "52759072B76D79FD"
			rewards: [{
				count: 12
				id: "7EA83E28C891ED4E"
				item: "naturesaura:gold_powder"
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "square"
			tasks: [{
