		{
			dependencies: ["3BF0D53D85B2A4CA"]
			description: [
				"  You thought gravel was just useless rubble cluttering your builds? Well, take &2four&r of them in your inventory and compress them into something called &8Packed Gravel&r. It sounds trivial, but it is the essence of an old craft: panning."
				""
				"  Now take that block and &aright-click directly&r on the &bwater surface&r of a river or lake. &cDo not&r aim at the block below, and do not be submerged. With a bit of luck, you will find tiny gold nuggets mixed in with the silt. Feel free to pretend you are a prospector... just do not expect to get rich overnight."
				""
				"&7&o— No, you are not buying a castle. But yes, you are going to need it.&r&r"
			]
			icon: "kubejs:packed_gravel"
			id: "2B403653AED97321"
			shape: "square"
			tasks: [
				{
					id: "3662E3AB8600AE38"
					item: "minecraft:gold_nugget"
					type: "item"
				}
				{
					id: "16B5799F3E411ABA"
