		{
			dependencies: ["3BF0D53D85B2A4CA"]
			description: [
				"  With wood, craft some stands, simple pillars meant to support your first ritual. It is a humble step, but consider this: even raw timber can become part of a mystical spectacle. "
				""
				"&7&o— Nothing like poorly cut wood to serve as the foundation of an entire ritual. Brilliant.&r&r"
