		{
			dependencies: ["48B564A472DBB217"]
			description: [
				"  Time to open another compendium: the Book of Natural Aura. Inside, you will find detailed information about aura itself, the invisible energy that bathes the world. Rituals consume aura, and if there is too much or too little of it, the environment may respond with beneficial or harmful effects. For now, do not worry about that; later on, you will gain the tools needed to measure and manipulate this balance."
				""
				"  Ah, and one more trick: when viewing a ritual recipe in the book, click the eye icon. It generates a projected blueprint that can be placed in the world with right-click, showing exactly where each block should go. Very helpful, until you are finally capable of understanding things on your own."
				""
				"&7&o— Do not trust that book too much. It pretends to be your guide, but it is already getting tired of you.&r&r"
			]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
				id: "patchouli:guide_book"
				tag: {
					"patchouli:book": "naturesaura:book"
				}
			}
			id: "497584693F232C18"
			rewards: [{
				id: "086E8AAD6D366A8C"
				item: {
					Count: 1
					id: "patchouli:guide_book"
					tag: {
						"patchouli:book": "naturesaura:book"
					}
				}
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "woodtier"
			size: 1.1d
			tasks: [{
				id: "1A002CEF6E9549D6"
