		}
		{
			dependencies: [
				"4BE69805DC9E253E"
				"4618E30363D2830E"
			]
			description: [
				"  A peculiar outcome of the offering ritual: instead of a Spirit of Calling, simply toss in a wrench. Somehow, the forces beyond interpret this as a request for something useful — quite literally."
				""
				"  It seems these entities appreciate function over symbolism. Or maybe they just have a sense of humor involving tools."
				""
				"&7&o— Look, I don’t actually know who’s answering this ritual. But it works, so let’s not question it.&r&r"
			]
			id: "3E6E088EDD954E6F"
			size: 1.2d
			tasks: [{
				id: "45AB68D21D1C0292"
				item: "kubejs:token_utility"
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Askin’ for Somethin’ Useful?"
			x: 3.5d
			y: 2.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["558AD48F5D4237AC"]
			description: [
				"  This modpack has its own way of presenting itself. This is one of the few moments where I, the author, speak to you directly — the one who decided to give my work a chance."
				""
				"  From here on, the quests will guide you through a narrative that speaks to you personally. You can expect a bit of humor, a touch of poetry, but also clear and objective explanations so you never feel lost."
				""
				"  It's important to say: progression here is linear, and the recipes are deeply connected to one another. If you prefer completely freeform packs, this one might not be ideal. But if you enjoy the idea of a journey with well-defined paths and carefully woven progression, I believe you'll feel right at home."
				""
				"  Every detail was crafted with care — from the smallest machines to custom mechanics built specifically for this pack. Everything exists to make the experience feel unique and integrated. If you happen to stumble upon the biography of a slightly unhinged engineer along the way, consider yourself very welcome."
				""
				"  The two quests above explain the structure of the pack in more detail. If you're unsure where to begin, I recommend starting with them."
				""
				"  Oh, and don't worry about the crafting table recipe — it may look strange at first, but I promise it's simple."
				""
				"  Good luck, have fun, and I sincerely hope you enjoy the journey ahead."
				""
				"  See you at the end of it. &l&a:)&r&r"
			]
