		{
			dependencies: ["042EC538643F435A"]
			description: [
				"  These shimmering bricks form part of the multiblock structure for the Natural Altar. Their design is deliberate — gold conducts aura well, and stone keeps it grounded."
				""
				"&7&o— It’s decorative. It’s functional. Pretend you always knew that.&r&r"
