		{
			dependencies: ["042EC538643F435A"]
			description: [
				"  The air itself is not empty — each realm carries an imprint of its nature, suspended as ambient aura. With the Bottle and Crock, you can capture that essence directly from the environment. Simply &ahold&r it and &aright-click&r while standing in the dimension whose aura you seek."
				""
				"  Each realm yields a different essence, and these will fuel rituals far beyond simple alchemy."
				""
				"&7&o— The world exhales; you just happen to have a jar.&r&r"
			]
			icon: "naturesaura:bottle_two_the_rebottling"
			id: "5FD7CCD89895AAAB"
