		{
			dependencies: ["7E88E307D7B20E6B"]
			description: [
				"  Your human senses are inadequate for reading the flow of aura — no amount of focus, meditation, or \"good vibes\" will change that. The Environmental Eye reveals the invisible levels around you, letting you see what the world offers and what you’ve already taken."
				""
				"  Use it to understand when it’s safe to draw power and when nature needs a moment to breathe."
				""
				"&7&o— Enlightenment sometimes comes in the shape of a lens.&r&r"
			]
			id: "2DA99CE16108C12A"
			shape: "square"
			tasks: [{
				id: "4F2B1FF27B190705"
				item: "naturesaura:eye"
